press conference after concluding a three-day visit to Angola.
</P>
<P>
The signing of the letter of intent is conducive to the
long-term peace and stability along their 1,650 km common border,
he said, adding that the Angolan government will make continuous
efforts to maintain mutual understanding and respect among the
two peoples.
</P>
