<TEXT>
<P>
BEIJING, June 16 (Xinhua) -- A seminar marking the centenary of
the birth of Zhang Tailei, one of the early leaders of the
Chinese Communist Party, was held here today.
</P>
<P>
State Vice-President Hu Jintao attended the meeting, and Zeng
Qinghong, secretary of the secretariat of the Central Committee of
the Communist Party of China (CPC), delivered a speech at the
meeting.
</P>
<P>
