began with the founding stage of the CPC, who was one of the
important leaders of the early CPC and founders of the Chinese
Communist Youth League.
</P>
<P>
Zhang had made great contributions to the Party's organization,
publicity and youth work, and his glorious achievements and lofty
spirit will be forever remembered by the Chinese people, Zeng
said.
</P>
<P>
Zhang was killed in the Guangzhou Uprising of 1927, at the age
of 29. 
